12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
14 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 2904 of Title 74, unless there
15 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
16 A. There is hereby created on January 1, 2026, to continue
17 until December 30, 2035, the Oklahoma Workforce Housing Council
18 within the Oklahoma Workforce Commission. The Council shall be
19 composed of fifteen (15) members. The members shall serve as
20 follows:
21 1. Five members shall be appointed by the Governor:
22 a. one shall be a person living in an urban area with a
23 population more than seventy-five thousand (75,000)
24
